	<h1 style="color: red; text-align: center; font-size: 50px; letter-spacing: 2px; word-spacing: 5px;">Amidst all the rumours and news that are quite a many times delusional, take a moment to know what actually this pandemic is about, compiled from various verified sources!</h1>
</div>

<div>
	<button onclick="return fetchdata('symptoms')" style="font-size: 30px; background-color: green; color: yellow; border-radius: 50px; width: 250px; outline: none;"> How It Starts </button>
</div>

